{"ja398:0.1":"Jataka ","ja398:0.2":"Sattakanipata ","ja398:0.3":"Kukkuvagga ","ja398:0.4":"3. Sutanujataka ","ja398:1.1":"“Raja te bhattam pahesi, ","ja398:1.2":"Sucim mamsupasecanam; ","ja398:1.3":"Maghadevasmim adhivatthe, ","ja398:1.4":"Ehi nikkhamma bhunjasu”. ","ja398:2.1":"“Ehi manava orena, ","ja398:2.2":"bhikkhamadaya supitam; ","ja398:2.3":"Tvanca manava bhikkha ca, ","ja398:2.4":"ubho bhakkha bhavissatha”. ","ja398:3.1":"“Appakena tuvam yakkha, ","ja398:3.2":"thullamattham jahissasi; ","ja398:3.3":"Bhikkham te naharissanti, ","ja398:3.4":"jana maranasannino. ","ja398:4.1":"Laddhaya yakkha tava niccabhikkham, ","ja398:4.2":"Sucim panitam rasasa upetam; ","ja398:4.3":"Bhikkhanca te ahariyo naro idha, ","ja398:4.4":"Sudullabho hehiti bhakkhite mayi”. ","ja398:5.1":"“Mameva sutano attho, ","ja398:5.2":"yatha bhasasi manava; ","ja398:5.3":"Maya tvam samanunnato, ","ja398:5.4":"sotthim passahi mataram. ","ja398:6.1":"Khaggam chattanca patinca, ","ja398:6.2":"gacchamadaya manava; ","ja398:6.3":"Sotthim passatu te mata, ","ja398:6.4":"tvanca passahi mataram”. ","ja398:7.1":"“Evam yakkha sukhi hohi, ","ja398:7.2":"saha sabbehi natibhi; ","ja398:7.3":"Dhananca me adhigatam, ","ja398:7.4":"ranno ca vacanam katan”ti. ","ja398:8.1":"Sutanujatakam tatiyam. "}